{"tid":325024,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[有鳩睇] 會員「雲雨」#42425 請找數 [369]","createTime":"2017-07-17T02:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T07:02:50.000Z","uid":76388,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a8e5a50e57227ce0cee05740a950519734452a","tid":325024,"uid":76388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，事緣係幾日前有巴打post 咗張 2017 DSE 中文2 其餘幾乎5** 嘅相<br />\nLink: <a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/320706/page/12\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/320706/page/12</a><br />\n<br />\n入面有巴打表示學中文根本就冇用（註：並非指DSE中文科）<br />\n我睇唔過眼反駁，點知就俾人屈話實係英文廢，淨係識攞中文打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我唯有利申自己幾年前考DSE 主科都有5* 以上，洗唔洗攞中文嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知 會員「<span style=\"color: red;\">雲雨</span>」亂入，表示我有5* 咁佢都有「30cm長 190 月入300k」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲話我有證據，就<span style=\"color: red;\">影碌鳩加名</span>俾我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/095838_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F095838_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=7ad1224c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁小弟唯有找數搵返張cert 俾佢睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/100111_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F100111_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=72193699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事隔一日幾，<span style=\"color: red;\">會員「雲雨」都仲未找數</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺其他post 見佢留言，追佢數都當睇我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家特登開post 希望「雲雨」快d 入嚟找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望我唔洗學佢狙擊人咁狙擊返佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/100753_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F100753_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=be43bb7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31c3aad8ec13c4af58aca4a1a7c902a08ab20910","tid":325024,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9a8fd5fa55cf369f31f16aa98d1b6fed9af0443","tid":325024,"uid":41112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6328727fdf85e510d45adc71bd7599cc423d9a","tid":325024,"uid":76388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學雞嘅鳩有咩好睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGay</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好睇 但數還數 都要找囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92f3b4b59eb983efc90f46e8bdffa032b917d80","tid":325024,"uid":76388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"都係學返佢狙擊人咁開post 咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7362d76eaef22e3f1eca9470439f64d12056919","tid":325024,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h